Package: ZarrDataFrame
Version: 0.0.0
Date: 2024-03-11
Title: Bioconductor-friendly Bindings for Zarr
Description: 
    Implements bindings for zarr store that are compatible with Bioconductor
    S4 data structures, namely the DataFrame and DelayedArray. This allows 
    Zarr-backed data to be easily used as data frames with arbitrary sets of columns
Authors@R:
